intent: 'Wire production.rb to force TLS and allowlist DORM_GUARD_HOST, with /up excluded
  from both the SSL redirect and host authorization so Kamal''s Thruster health probe
  can reach the app over plain HTTP inside the container before TLS is issued.

  '
